text: Giants in the Trees are an American rock band formed in Wahkiakum County, Washington in 2017. It was founded by former Nirvana bass player Krist Novoselic. ==Albums== *Giants in the Trees (2017) *Volume 2 (2019) == References == Category:2010s American music groups Category:American rock bands Category:2017 establishments in the United States Category:Musical groups from Washington (state)
title: Giants in the Trees
